  Need more help?
%p.govuk-body
  If you think that you need some extra help to keep you independent at home, you can contact
  = link_to "Essex County Council Adult Social Care", "https://www.essex.gov.uk/Health-Social-Care/Pages/Health-and-Social-Care.aspx", target: :_blank, class: "govuk-link govuk-body"
  for an assessment of your needs.
%p.govuk-body
  Most people have to pay something towards their care.
  = link_to "Find out how Essex County Council", "https://www.essex.gov.uk/Health-Social-Care/Health-and-social-care-for-adults/charging-for-care-services/Pages/Default.aspx", target: :_blank, class: "govuk-link govuk-body"
  works out how much you will be asked to pay.

